### Issue description

重载父类的 getter / setter
```ts
export class NewComponent extends Component {

    get enabled () {
        return this._enabled;
    }

    set enabled (v: boolean) {
        super.enabled = v;
        console.warn("test info")
    }
}
```

构建之后，super 会编译成  this 导致调用栈溢出
```js
        _createClass(NewComponent, [{
          key: "enabled",
          get: function get() {
            return this._enabled;
          },
          set: function set(v) {
            this.enabled = v;
            console.warn("test info");
          }
        }]);
```

补充：web 预览没有这个问题

