### Issue description

**Expected Result:**
Nested properties should behave in the same way than root properties in the animation system.

**Actual Result:**
Nested properties are not interpolated properly at first, but become interpolated after resaving the animation clip with another modification.




### Relevant error log output

**Content of .anim file on first save (step 7 in reproduction steps) :**
